# WebCLI release promote

When the user needs changes on the live release (`:8787` / phone), **you** run
`promote-to-release.bat` from the repo root. Do not tell them to restart
manually.

Schedule promote as the **last** step of the turn, then stop — the current run
blocks idle restart if you keep polling. Details: skill `promote-web-cli-release`.
